	<div class="grid-article-bd">
		<h1 class="smart-dotdotdot">巴菲特出手之后，各类投资人会如何评估苹果公司的股票？</h1>
	</div>
	<div class="grid-article-ft  clearfix">
		<span class="smart-date" data-originDate="2016-05-22 07:22:03 +0800"></span>
		<div class="ribbon">
				<span class="iconfont icon-heart">11</span>
		</div>
	</div>
</a>

                    </div>
                    <div class="packery-item article">
                        <!-- 普通文章格子，占位1x1，智能占位 -->
<!-- 传入参数：article -->

<a href="/articles/27169.html" class="com-grid-article" >
	<div class="grid-article-hd">
		<img class="pic lazyload" data-src="/system/articles/articleshows/27169/indexMediumPc2/27169.jpg?1463873325" alt="其实在 YouTube 上，人们只看少数的那几个视频">
		
		<p class="category">
			<img src="/system/categories/iconwhites/3/medium/3.png?1411569578" alt="娱乐">
			<span>娱乐</span>
		</p>
